org.apache.flex.abc.print

Class ABCDumpVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.abc.PoolingABCVisitor
      • org.apache.flex.abc.print.ABCDumpVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IABCVisitor, IVisitor

    public class ABCDumpVisitor
extends PoolingABCVisitor
    ABC Visitor implementation that can take an ABC and dump out a textual representation of it. Similar to abcdump/abcdis in the tamarin project.

    To use, construct one of these and pass it ABCParser, or whatever is driving the ABC events.
